			<div STYLE="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; line-height: 23.636363983154297px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: auto !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
<img src="http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src ="http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/a1929b37jw1ew5wzr2sdhj21hc0u0456.jpg" STYLE="border-style: none; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; padding: 5px 0px; word-wrap: break-word !important;"  ALT="保卫台湾：日军侵占台湾的死伤人数两倍于甲午战争"  TITLE="保卫台湾：日军侵占台湾的死伤人数两倍于甲午战争" />&nbsp;<wbr><span STYLE="max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">2014</SPAN><span STYLE="max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">年5月30日，台湾老中青三代保钓人士高举着“莫忘甲午耻”的旗帜，用“路过”铭传大学的方式纪念甲午战争120周年。他们期盼能够唤起台湾大众对钓鱼台（岛）主权的重视，正是甲午战争的惨败让日本趁机窃取了钓鱼台（岛）。今天，台湾保钓义士们继承了120年前台湾人民用鲜血与生命保卫台湾的不屈精神，坚守着民族尊严。</SPAN></DIV>
<div STYLE="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; line-height: 23.636363983154297px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: auto !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
<span STYLE="max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">
<br STYLE="word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></SPAN></DIV>
<p STYLE="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; line-height: 23.636363983154297px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: auto !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
<span STYLE="max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">
历史不容忘记！</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; line-height: 23.636363983154297px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: auto !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
<span STYLE="max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">
让我们一起回到<span STYLE="max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;">100</SPAN>多年前，去追寻台湾人民保卫国土浴血抗战的历史足迹。</SPAN></P>
